properties.headline: FLOODING FORBES TO BACK CREEK Newell Highway CLOSED
properties.diversions:
Diversion for all vehicles up to 26m B-Doubles:

Northbound from West Wyalong to Forbes: Mid Western Hwy, Henry Lawson Way, Lachlan Valley Way, Reymond St, Flint St and Bridge St

Southbound from Forbes to West Wyalong: Wirrinya Rd, Red Bend Rd, Wongajong Rd, Lachlan Valley Way, Henry Lawson Way and Mid Western Hwy 

Diversion for vehicles greater than 26m B-Doubles:

Northbound from Finely: Riverina Hwy to Deniliquin, Cobb Hwy to Hay, Sturt Hwy to Buronga, Silver City Hwy to Broken Hill, Barrier Hwy to Nyngan, and Mitchell Hwy to Dubbo.

Southbound from Dubbo: Mitchell Hwy to Nyngan, Barrier Hwy to Broken Hill, Silver City Hwy to Buronga, Sturt Hwy to Hay, Cobb Hwy to Deniliquin, and Riverina Hwy to Finely.

NOTE for PBS Operators

PBS vehicles over 26m are not automatically required to take the routes marked for prescriptive vehicles over 26m. The Performance Based Standards (PBS) map should be consulted to determine if the up to 26m B Double detour is an approved route for PBS based on mass and vehicle type. This map now has a flood layer (updated hourly) allowing operators to view current State Road closures impacting the PBS network.

Diversion for vehicles operating under the Class 1 Load Carrying Notice:

Northbound from West Wyalong: Newell Hwy and Mid Western Hwy to Cowra, Canowindra Rd to Cudal, The Escort Way and Peabody Rd to Molong, and the Mitchell Hwy to Dubbo.

Southbound from Dubbo: Mitchell Hwy to Molong, Peabody Rd and The Escort Way to Cudal, Canowindra Rd to Cowra, and Mid Western Hwy to re-join the Newell Hwy at Back Creek.
